##How to install hexo 
1.Install nvm according to the following instruct:

	wget -qO- https://raw.github.com/creationix/nvm/master/install.sh | sh
	nvm install 0.10

after that please reboot your terminal.
2.Install hexo 

	npm install hexo@2.8.3 -g
	npm install hexo-renderer-marked@0.1
	npm install hexo-renderer-stylus@0.1

after that you can use it.
3.how to use it simplely

	hexo init hexo
	hexo g
	hexo s

